txt.en: The White Hand Orcs of Fushaum-dorám have raised banners in their triumph over Scylfig. You should tear them down.
The White Hand Orcs of Fushaum-dorám have raised banners in their triumph over Scylfig. You should tear them down.
White Hand Banners can be found at Fushaum-dorám in the south-eastern Writhendowns.\n\nYou should destroy the banners of the Orcs to weaken their pleasure in their victory at Scylfig.
